<head>HUMAN DIGNITY</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">人的尊嚴</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>NOBILITY in ALL HUMANS that CAUSES them to DESERVE APPROPRIATE BASIC RESPECT AND FREEDOMS.</p>
<p>[[MENSCHENWUERDE]]</p>
